{"tid":1398020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港人對過期TG好似冇乜反應","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T20:03:51.000Z","uid":43231,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6baae862cf869cac16c05ac01ba80347bf7f1091","tid":1398020,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"班狗唔理通例就係人都知，下下民居Tear Gas放題，唔關事既都中晒招，但係講緊既過期tear gas <span style=\"color: red;\">後遺症：確診嘅化學性肺炎（chemical pneumonitis）、頭痛、不停咳、失聲、心口/肺部痛、反覆肚瀉（呢個好多人有）、大量紅疹、化學𤆥傷，等等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">過期後既TG會化成山埃毒氣，仲有人話會致盲。</span>而家各區都有遊行加後續活動，難保有日你係屋企都會食晒，咦香港人平時食二手煙都屌晒鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家點解冇乜反應？而家仲夠唔夠膽講政治唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於過期既tear gas post唔該推返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[唔該全部同我入嚟]過期催淚彈一定要煲大佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395445</a><br />\n<br />\n[超危急] 食過過期催淚彈嘅手足注意！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394990</a><br />\n<br />\n【 香港可能面對緊一場極大嘅人道災難 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394867</a>"},{"pid":"639940083d6867282de48e6dfbeb4757d02df943","tid":1398020,"uid":41292,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"Tg 我以為係telegram <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.5 全民三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" cla